Abstractions:
        ->The process of hiding the implementation details and showing only the essential features or
          functionality of an object, achieved using abstract classes and interfaces.


Ex: UPI payments we are just scanning and paying to the user the money deduction and credited from one
    bank to another bank background process how it happen we dont get to know

Ex using abstract class:
          ->It may contain:
          ->Abstract methods (methods without a body)
          ->Concrete methods (methods with implementation)
          ->Constructors
          ->Instance variables
          ->Static and final methods


          public abstract class UpiPayments{
            abstract void upiPayment(double money);

            public void paymentStatus(String status){
            System.out.println("payment status "+ status);
            }

          }




